flowchart LR
    A[Login] --> B[Dashboard]
    B --> C[Holdings List]
    B --> D[Watchlist / Cumsun]
    B --> E[Sources: CEX/Wallet]
    B --> F[Settings]

    C --> C1[Asset Detail]
    C1 --> C2[Riwayat Transaksi]
    C1 --> C3[Tambah Transaksi]

    D --> D1[Tambah ke Watchlist]
    D --> D2[Convert ke Holding]
    D2 --> C3

    E --> E1[Tambah Sumber Baru]
    E --> E2["Edit / Hapus Sumber (soft delete)"]

    F --> F1[Pilih Mata Uang Utama]
    F --> F2[Atur Kurs]
